metadata.title: CVE-2011-2335 on Ubuntu 14.04 LTS (trusty) - medium
metadata.description: A double-free vulnerability exists in WebKit in Google Chrome before BlinkM12 in the WebCore::CSSSelector function.

criterions.comment: webkitgtk: while related to the CVE in some way, a decision has been made to ignore this issue (note: 'end of standard support').
